{"type": "article", "id": 22820, "title": "Facebook 扑克牌", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-25T07:36:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606153547IBJC5ipz3eqDkNGm.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是英国一家平面设计公司 Human After All 推出的扑克牌，他们受到 Facebook 的邀请设计一幅能提供市场信息的牌。在简洁的图案下面都配合了一排文字，52 张牌提供的信息都不一样，比如“多达 25% 的电视观众在看电视的同时也在使用 Facebook”或者“41% 的英国人说他们从  11 月就开始购买圣诞”。这些信息就像 Facebook 上会传递的信息一样，可以让从未接触的人多一份认知和亲近，而对于老用户来说也是有纪念意义的收藏品。<a href=\"http://www.humanafterall.co.uk/work/projects/b2b-playing-cards/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061535438LZcoieIPxAOTwg5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153544ya01vzfh8QEZ6Rsp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061535444Y82b5kFo0yTwjfL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061535453ENKrk9o6mdYjqil.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061535451B0eACdcm7j4JtbU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153546vJMZjEql86CNzQwx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}